                                            <td align="left" style="padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; background-color: #fff;" class="padding-copy">
                                                <h2>Why Require MFA?</h2>
                                                <p>MFA is an essential service to help safeguard access to critical systems or systems storing sensitive and research data. This added level of security substantially reduces the likelihood of unauthorized access to sensitive information through the use of compromised NetIDs.</p>
                                                <h2>Support</h2>
                                                <p>Have questions about using the i4 server? Explore the tutorials and FAQs available in the <a href="https://www.nyu.edu/employees/resources-and-services/media-and-communications/digital-communications/web-guide.html" style="color: #57068c;">NYU Web Guide</a> or contact the <a href="mailto:webteam@nyu.edu" style="color: #57068c;">Web Team</a>.</p>
